title: The Inside Crew Reacts to Ben Simmons'  Game 7 Performance Against the Atlanta Hawks | NBA on TNT
author: NBA on TNT
description:
After the Philadelphia 76ers were eliminated by the Atlanta Hawks in Game 7, the Inside guys break down Ben Simmons' performance and his future.
